The doctor said

51
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,430
it might be the academic pressure

52
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:19,750
of middle school.

53
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:22,240
It could also be adolescence-related.

54
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:23,710
And the doctor said

55
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:26,310
even kids who seem cheerful

56
00:02:27,030 --> 00:02:28,870
aren't immune to this illness.

57
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:30,910
I...

58
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:33,240
I've failed as a father.

59
00:02:40,470 --> 00:02:41,240
