119
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,360
Ms. Zhou,

120
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:13,000
I invited you here today

121
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,360
just to tell you

122
00:05:15,270 --> 00:05:16,830
Dong is a fraud.

123
00:05:16,830 --> 00:05:17,720
