140
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:51,040
Me blowing kisses to her?

141
00:05:52,660 --> 00:05:54,560
Oh my!

142
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,310
Yesterday.

143
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:57,510
- You forgot your phone when going out.
- Listen.

144
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:59,680
