195
00:07:39,310 --> 00:07:40,240
Where's makeup?

196
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:41,120
Let's check the equipment.

197
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:41,560
Put it here

198
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:43,040
Hurry up, we're in a rush.

199
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,390
Done, all set.

200
00:07:44,950 --> 00:07:45,390
Pull this wire.

201
00:07:45,390 --> 00:07:45,920
Double-check it.

202
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:46,430
Right.

203
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,360
The board.

204
00:07:48,630 --> 00:07:49,390
I'm good here.

205
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:12,510
Ms. Zhou, I'm truly sorry.

206
00:08:14,510 --> 00:08:16,750
We...we meant well but messed up.

207
00:08:17,750 --> 00:08:18,430
