236
00:09:39,870 --> 00:09:40,630
Do tell.

237
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,030
As long as I can do it,

238
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:43,200
I'll give it my all.

239
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,510
You know what Dong

240
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,720
is like.

241
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,360
All these years

242
00:09:49,790 --> 00:09:51,030
