249
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,080
What do you think we should do?

250
00:10:08,510 --> 00:10:10,480
Ms. Zhou, you mean...

251
00:10:11,550 --> 00:10:13,270
I'm nearly 20 years older than him.

252
00:10:13,790 --> 00:10:15,670
